           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS AND COCV6320-CTIPO NOT EQUAL SPACES
              MOVE CON-CTABELA-CTIPO
                TO WS-CTABELA
              MOVE COCV6320-CTIPO
                TO WS-CCOD
              MOVE SPACES
